Note that 
Kvutil.pm and kvget_metadata have their own packages.

Copy from this catalogue to the right directories in the debian package:
cp -pv control   $Packageroot/DEBIAN
cp -pv copyright $Packageroot/usr/share/doc/kvalobs-metadata
cp -pv changelog $Packageroot/usr/share/doc/kvalobs-metadata/changelog

After that "gzip --best" the changelog file 